    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LET'S GO ROOKIE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the boots of Jax, a rookie in the legendary 'Star Gunners' squadron. When your team vanishes over an uncharted planet, shot down by a mysterious enemy, all you have is their distress signal. Now, it's your chance to prove yourself. Embark on an explosive, bullet-hell adventure through a vibrant, interconnected world full of exploration and danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/b8c58538db406a8fa6021cc1296b9e6d.poster.avif?t=1748939075\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/b8c58538db406a8fa6021cc1296b9e6d.webm?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/b8c58538db406a8fa6021cc1296b9e6d.mp4?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SAVE YOUR SQUAD!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle through intense dungeons to rescue your teammates and claim their powerful Star Gunner abilities! Glide on water, wield a laser samurai sword, unleash super strength, and more as you unlock tougher areas. Explore lush alien fields, neon crystal caves, and thorny swamps in your epic adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/3100fedb3e46a11d43cc909c9b2cecd0.poster.avif?t=1748939075\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/3100fedb3e46a11d43cc909c9b2cecd0.webm?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/3100fedb3e46a11d43cc909c9b2cecd0.mp4?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMBAT CARNAGE!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic twin stick combat with a growing roster of powerups and upgrades. Use your skills to dash through dangerous encounters or use your shield to defend against the onslaught. Swift and responsive controls for both newcomers and veterans alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/c0de5cae237e998d54c648fcedcea010.poster.avif?t=1748939075\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/c0de5cae237e998d54c648fcedcea010.webm?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/c0de5cae237e998d54c648fcedcea010.mp4?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADES!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue captives and use their skills to build facilities that enhance your adventure! Upgrade stats, expand power-ups, and increase rocket count. To upgrade everything, earn big by dominating the battlefield!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/5738f0710e5b497ba8035726ad841b49.poster.avif?t=1748939075\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/5738f0710e5b497ba8035726ad841b49.webm?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/5738f0710e5b497ba8035726ad841b49.mp4?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RETRO FLAVOUR!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey back to the golden era of action-packed 90s cartoons with an adventure that captures the magic of retro classics. Inspired by our nostalgia for the N64 and PS1 days, this game blends hand-painted artistry with that unmistakable 90s attitude, wrapping you in a warm, familiar glow. We cherish those past adventures, so here's one crafted with love for the future!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/077e2b4bf371c3e20a5c8f9e7f3f4aba.poster.avif?t=1748939075\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/077e2b4bf371c3e20a5c8f9e7f3f4aba.webm?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3005330/extras/077e2b4bf371c3e20a5c8f9e7f3f4aba.mp4?t=1748939075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Star Gunners is still in early development and subject to changes. I am excited to share more as development progresses. Please be sure to wishlist and follow Star Gunners for update.</i></p>",
